{"tid":1473013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新西蘭外交部：制定應急計劃　必要時撤離在香港國民","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:47:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a893026d095a67b7728e12772751428955a12771","tid":1473013,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波持續，大批示威者昨（13日）堵塞機場離境大堂，不少航班取消，並於晚上爆發警民衝突。新西蘭外交及貿易部今日（14日）表示，因應香港局勢惡化，已制定應急計劃，必要時會撤離在港的新西蘭人。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道指出，正計劃前往香港的新西蘭人被告知需與航空公司聯繫，再次確認行程。"},{"pid":"1546b44d30478a637b717befaa6b94f81a59b241","tid":1473013,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗無撞鬼 而係高層係想借機會令所有狗都沾上鮮血<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHpLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHpLS</a>"},{"pid":"84b4c1b5987228f45434ad0c9146c24ccc59b13f","tid":1473013,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"世界大戰抺黑宇宙了~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a85bb97367d7aa690b42c39853eca594578827","tid":1473013,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"呢招正過譴責"},{"pid":"598e153acfc20723e568485ac3ed104395a620f9","tid":1473013,"uid":276989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"外國撤僑民最多咪幾日完事，撤資更簡單，現金禁個制就流走，股票物業大幅貶值拋售<br />\n<br />\n解放軍入城先決條件係有第二個城市可以取締香港，可惜無，因為上海自帶解放軍"},{"pid":"aeefb0c02beb1e427dd07f0ab6b024acc9fc0244","tid":1473013,"uid":169741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"外國撒僑意味愈來愈近出老解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af559170a7377c5be